00:01:32,134 --> 00:01:37,338
So Mafia III is an upholdment game on organized crime set

30
00:01:37,479 --> 00:01:42,803
in 1968 in a city called New Bordeaux, Louisiana, USA,

31
00:01:43,163 --> 00:01:45,365
inspired by the real city of New Orleans.

32
00:01:46,606 --> 00:01:50,429
You play the game as Lincoln Clay, a Vietnam veteran who

33
00:01:50,469 --> 00:01:52,450
wages war on the local mafia.

34
00:01:54,369 --> 00:01:57,510
In Mafia 3, after being betrayed by the mob,

35
00:01:57,731 --> 00:02:00,152
you have to conquer three districts from the Mafia,

36
00:02:00,792 --> 00:02:03,793
which enables you to collaborate with three underbosses.

37
00:02:04,514 --> 00:02:07,215
Vito, the main protagonist from Mafia 2,

38
00:02:07,875 --> 00:02:08,835
here on the left,

39
00:02:09,936 --> 00:02:12,377
and two major new characters in the franchise,

40
00:02:12,717 --> 00:02:15,058
Burke, on top here, and Cassandra.

41
00:02:16,059 --> 00:02:18,460
Lincoln, the hero, is on the right.

42
00:02:20,617 --> 00:02:22,759
So after all the underbosses have been unlocked,

43
00:02:23,219 --> 00:02:25,721
your objective is to conquer six new districts,

44
00:02:26,341 --> 00:02:29,624
which you can allocate to any of the three underbosses.

45
00:02:32,286 --> 00:02:35,368
