906
00:49:34,040 --> 00:49:36,483
In short, the takeaways from this presentation.

907
00:49:37,584 --> 00:49:39,966
Define and know your constraints well.

908
00:49:40,306 --> 00:49:42,308
Here, I needed to find interesting rules

909
00:49:43,249 --> 00:49:44,670
around territory division.

910
00:49:46,472 --> 00:49:48,794
Define the basic concepts that you want to explore.

911
00:49:49,174 --> 00:49:52,858
When you need an update, revisit these basic concepts

912
00:49:52,938 --> 00:49:55,020
and see how you can improve the execution.

913
00:49:56,694 --> 00:49:59,176
Prototype, learn, implement, and iterate.

914
00:49:59,656 --> 00:50:03,019
It takes a while to get comfortable with a design,

915
00:50:03,679 --> 00:50:06,381
to know it, and to know how to mature it.

